      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="重灌清單"><a href="#重灌清單" class="headerlink" title="重灌清單"></a>重灌清單</h1><h2 id="作業系統"><a href="#作業系統" class="headerlink" title="作業系統"></a>作業系統</h2><p>主力: Windows 10 專業版(1709)<br>選擇: Windows 10 家用版(1709)</p><h2 id="軟體清單"><a href="#軟體清單" class="headerlink" title="軟體清單"></a>軟體清單</h2><h3 id="雲端儲存"><a href="#雲端儲存" class="headerlink" title="雲端儲存"></a>雲端儲存</h3><p><a href="https://www.google.com/intl/zh-TW_ALL/drive/download/backup-and-sync/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google backup-and-sync</a></p><h3 id="瀏覽器"><a href="#瀏覽器" class="headerlink" title="瀏覽器"></a>瀏覽器</h3><ol><li><a href="https://www.google.com.tw/chrome/browser/desktop/index.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Chrome</a></li><li><a href="https://www.mozilla.org/zh-TW/firefox/new/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">FireFox</a><h3 id="文書工具"><a href="#文書工具" class="headerlink" title="文書工具"></a>文書工具</h3></li><li>Windows Office 2013(看要不要升級2016)<h3 id="檔案總管"><a href="#檔案總管" class="headerlink" title="檔案總管"></a>檔案總管</h3></li><li><a href="http://www.softwareok.com/?seite=Freeware/Q-Dir&amp;language=english" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Q-DIR</a><h3 id="開發工具"><a href="#開發工具" class="headerlink" title="開發工具"></a>開發工具</h3></li><li>Visual Studio 2015(<a href="https://www.visualstudio.com/zh-hant/downloads/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">2017</a>) Enterprise<br>外掛工具：<ol><li>Productivity Power Tools<br><img src="https://i.imgur.com/kdKZ6VR.png" alt=""><br><img src="https://i.imgur.com/JW4FJKr.png" alt=""></li><li>Indent Guides</li><li>GitDiffMargin</li></ol></li><li><a href="https://notepad-plus-plus.org/download" target="_blank" rel="noopener">NotePad++</a></li><li><a href="https://www.microsoft.com/zh-tw/sql-server/sql-server-downloads" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SQL Server Developer Edition</a> + <a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/zh-tw/sql/ssms/download-sql-server-management-studio-ssms" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SSMS</a><br>外掛工具<ol><li><a href="https://www.red-gate.com/products/sql-development/sql-prompt/index" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SQL Prompt</a></li><li>SQL Complete(選用)</li></ol></li><li>Enterprise Architect</li></ol><h3 id="版控工具"><a href="#版控工具" class="headerlink" title="版控工具"></a>版控工具</h3><ol><li><a href="https://gitforwindows.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Git for Windows</a></li><li><a href="https://tortoisegit.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TortoiseGit</a>(操作比較方便)</li><li><a href="https://www.sourcetreeapp.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">SourceTree</a>(比較好看差異)</li><li><a href="https://tortoisesvn.net/downloads.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TortoiseSVN</a>(舊專案用)</li></ol><h3 id="截圖工具"><a href="#截圖工具" class="headerlink" title="截圖工具"></a>截圖工具</h3><ol><li><a href="http://www.azofreeware.com/2009/01/picpick-1802.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">PicPick</a></li></ol><h3 id="遠端連線"><a href="#遠端連線" class="headerlink" title="遠端連線"></a>遠端連線</h3><ol><li><a href="https://www.teamviewer.com/zhtw/download/windows/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">TeamViewer</a><br><a href="https://www.teamviewer.com/zhtw/download/previous-versions/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">舊版</a></li></ol><p><img src="https://i.imgur.com/VZHjlqe.png" alt=""></p>]]></content>
      
      
